				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A dialogue with one of the \"guards\" in House of Hope. \r\nThese are Eternal Debtors, each one has a story how did they manage to get into Raphael's hands. \r\n\r\nThese characters see players as \"debtors\" of House of Hope as well and they don't usually know anything about players. "
